<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A tlaumi a kawl, nem te'n an auh hna, Tlangsang cung a vakvaimi hna
 zong, &quot;Bawipa aw nih ka sin ra u,&quot; a ti Atu zongah Bawipa nih an auh.

[C1]
   Lam hlatnak le, tlang sannak zongin, A vakvaimi ratpi hna u (pi hna
   u), Khamhtu hruangchung le a inn chungah. A tlaumi kha luhpi hna u, luhpi
   hna u.

[V2]
 A tlaumi kawl tuah, Bawipa Jesuh ca'h, Thlarau der le lungkuaimi hna
 kha, Khamhnak lam ah hruai zungzal ko hna law; Nun dongh lonak hmun ah
 kalter hna.

[C2]
   Lam hlatnak le, tlang sannak zongin, A vakvaimi ratpi hna u (pi hna
   u), Khamhtu hruangchung le a inn chungah. A tlaumi kha luhpi hna u, luhpi
   hna u.

[V3]
 Velngeihnak thawng chim in kal lengmang tuah, Nitin Bawipa Khrih zul
 lengmang ko, A rilmi hlawm hna, a dermi hnem hna; Lam le nunnak Bawi
 Jesuh panh in.

[C3]
   Lam hlatnak le, tlang sannak zongin, A vakvaimi ratpi hna u (pi hna
   u), Khamhtu hruangchung le a inn chungah. A tlaumi kha luhpi hna u, luhpi
   hna u.</lyrics>
<title>ZA TLAUMI A KAWL CH111</title>
<hymn_number>111</hymn_number>
</song>